column5: there are some really crazy talented people out there    I tried the walking on water one when was young......    all I can say is... jesus christ it didn't work........
Thats ok Terry.  The ones that try stuff and cant do it are funny too.
The 'running on water', also called liquid mountaineering, has been exposed as fake.
The guy in the wheel chair right at the start!!
Pretty tough to pick one, it's all pretty amazing.
